Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:42.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hope you understand, Miroku!\NWe can't take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:43.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:46.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Still, we can't just abandon her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.27,0:01:49.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- {\i1}We found her!{\i0}\N- {\i1}It's Koharu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:56.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Feudal Era...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.75,0:02:00.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Koharu had lost her parents\nand siblings in the war...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:04.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and was put to work day and night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:06.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:08.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here, eat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:12.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A younger Miroku who came\nto the village to perform an exorcism...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:13.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}met Koharu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:22.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Miroku, we just met again.\NAnd to be parted so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:24.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please understand, Koharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:30.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When it comes time to battle,\NI'm not sure I'll be able to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:35.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demon I seek is that formidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:43.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koharu, you're starting a new life\nin a new village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:46.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know you're scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.13,0:02:51.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To survive is scary, for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:58.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In my right hand is a hole that will\nsuck up everything and anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:01.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A Wind Tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:05.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A curse was put upon us\nduring my grandfather's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:07.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And that grandfather\nand then my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:10.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,were sucked up by the Wind Tunnels\nin their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:15.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In time, I, too,\nwill be sucked up by this hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:20.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I made the decision to live\nwith this curse as my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:26.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,One human taking on demons\nwith the Wind Tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:32.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This Wind Tunnel is a weapon\ngiven to me. That's what I decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:39.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku is trembling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:44.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A lie... Is what he just told me a lie?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:50.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To live strong is very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:56.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To overcome uncertainty\nis an enormous task.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:17.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were looking for a new place\nfor Koharu to live...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:21.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}when villagers whose souls had\nbeen stolen came and attacked us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.66,0:04:22.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:33.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha is forced to fight them\nwithout hurting them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:37.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango is hit by her own Hiraikotsu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:44.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A ghostly white demon steals away\NKoharu's soul and mine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:49.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone be careful!\NWatch out for that mirror!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:14.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Her soul does not fit in...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:20.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you cannot move, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:24.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The fragment of the Sacred Jewel\nwhich Kagome holds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:26.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:36.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:40.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:50.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:53.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where is Kagome?\NShippo! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:00.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's still moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:04.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango! Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:06.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is she the one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:17.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome! Kagome! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:21.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara! Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:23.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:25.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo!\NWhat happened here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:28.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A white demon appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:31.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome's soul\nwas sucked into that mirror of hers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:33.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Her soul was sucked into the mirror?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:41.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're in the way! Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dance of the Wind Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:59.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Inuyasha?\NYou keep running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:05.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does that mean that you're not\nfully recovered from your wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:07.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}One attack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:10.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I can get one good swing,\nthis arm can handle it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:15.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Prepare to die!\NI avenge my comrades!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:21.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I fought that fool Koga\nwho was tricked by Naraku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:23.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:25.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My right arm was wounded...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:28.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}by the power\nof that fake Sacred Jewel fragment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:33.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That wound hasn't completely healed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:38.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, if I can cut through the\NWind Scar in one sweep I can beat her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:59.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never imagined this kid\nwould try to use something fancy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:02.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}like the Wind Scar to battle me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:11.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That time when we first fought the\nsacred arrow disrupted my wind flow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:14.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I ended up creating a Wind Scar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:21.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This arrow,\nit's purifying my ghostly wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:27.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I knew it!\NThe ghostly wind has disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:30.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool! Wind is easily created!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:40.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Wind Scar is created\nwhen the ghostly winds collide.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:45.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I control all wind!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:52.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If not for that arrow\na Wind Scar would never have formed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:05.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't, it's not working.\NInside this wind which she controls...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:07.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}a Wind Scar will not form.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:16.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:19.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No mistake... that {\i1}was{\i0} a Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:23.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?!\NIs the control of the wind weakening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:27.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:32.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can slay her now with the Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:35.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is wielding the Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He intends to cut through\nthe Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:44.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! Inuyasha isn't aware of\nthe existence of that white demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just as Sango's Hiraikotsu\nwas thrust back at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:50.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha's Tetsusaiga will be thrown!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:53.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- I can see it!\N- I allowed you to see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:57.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Wind Scar!\N- Want to cut through?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:00.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:07.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:14.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:46.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:48.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:19.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:21.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:28.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was quite easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:32.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I came here personally\nto ask how you felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:35.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,having your power\nturned back so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:40.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My, you mean,\nwe are honored by the man himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:43.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and not some death doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:46.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're a coward\nwho never sullies his hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:49.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who only knows\nhow to lay traps, nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:52.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you must have been quite confident\nabout your trick this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:54.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:58.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're free to do as you please\nand suck up everything in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:03.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But monk,\nsurely you are not {\i1}that{\i0} foolish?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:08.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The souls of Kagome and\nthe villagers are locked in that mirror.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:09.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:14.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All I did was create Wind and Void\nas offshoots of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:17.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And look at all the damage\nyou suffered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:19.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:20.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Offshoots?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:25.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, Naraku's power has increased\nto the level of this kind of sorcery.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:29.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've fought Kagura\nthe Wind Sorceress once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:34.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the other is Void?\NSo it has no presence, no scent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:38.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No wonder we didn't realize it\nuntil it was too late.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:41.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Hang on! Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:49.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:55.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara, please take me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:59.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take me to Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:01.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Haven't we talked enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:05.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall we take Inuyasha's head\nwith us then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.11,0:13:08.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:12.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Weren't you going to tell that woman\nthat Inuyasha has been killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:16.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's what I thought you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:22.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,True. It was only through\nthat woman's cooperation...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:24.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that I was able to create\nyou and Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:30.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd like to see her face when\NI show her Inuyasha's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:34.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's the meaning of this?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:36.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku's Sacred Jewel fragment\nis nearly whole!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.18,0:13:41.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mentioned earlier\nthat I don't dirty my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:45.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, even at the top,\nthere's someone higher up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:51.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There is a woman who used me,\NNaraku, in order to kill Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:52.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Woman?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can't be!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:57.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Some woman... this Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:00.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:05.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, Inuyasha! You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:10.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo personally handed this\NSacred Jewel fragment to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:15.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:21.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And she's eager to see\nyour dead face!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.06,0:14:27.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo! Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:30.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:32.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hand over your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:44.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome's arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:45.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:55.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That girl!\NKanna, you failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:58.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That girl is still moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:03.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her soul is spilling out of the mirror.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:07.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does this girl have such a large soul?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:14.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:17.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:19.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How is Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:24.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's still breathing.\NBut he's hurt all over and can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:28.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:35.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so glad...\NI'm so glad Inuyasha is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:39.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But how did this happen?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:43.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}How did Naraku get a hold\nof that Sacred Jewel fragment?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:53.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the very one that Kikyo\nstole away from me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:16:01.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It must have been Kikyo\nwho gave Naraku that fragment!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:09.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo gave him the fragment\nwhich we all worked so hard to collect.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:12.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}However...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:18.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even after she did a dastardly thing,\NInuyasha still loves Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:25.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even after being so badly wounded,\nhe can't forget about Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:30.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Woman, give this message\nto Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:33.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If he must hate, hate Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:37.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha's death is Kikyo's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:42.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Every time I listen to you.\NI start to feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.26,0:16:45.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,really sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:47.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:50.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just as the Tetsusaiga was deflected,\nyour arrow will be do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:52.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:57.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My arrow only goes after bad people!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:26.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:32.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The sacred arrow\nis being swallowed up by the mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:40.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I couldn't deflect Kagome's arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:44.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong!?\NWhy can't you deflect it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:49.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The arrow is made out of soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:53.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The mirror is filled to the brim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:59.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Unless the souls are released,\nthe mirror will burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:33.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone has gotten their souls back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:36.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, the Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:37.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:41.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.48,0:18:42.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:43.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:46.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:52.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To survive is scary, for everyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:58.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}In my right hand is a hole that will\nsuck up everything and anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:03.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}In time, I, too,\nwill be sucked up by this hole.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:08.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To live strong is very difficult.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:13.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To overcome uncertainty\nis an enormous task.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:33.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're swift to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:38.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll let you live for a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.27,0:19:46.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel will continue\nto give me new powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:48.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let us all enjoy it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:52.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the immeasurable power\nof the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:10.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, what're we all doing\nin a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.97,0:20:13.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My mind is in a daze.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:14.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:51.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Hey, cheer up, will you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:56.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is what I'd like to say.\NBut I guess not this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:21:00.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku has collected nearly all\nof the Sacred Jewel fragments.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:05.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, no! We can't be so weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:07.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all in how you see things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:10.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We fought a Naraku\nwho has amassed such power...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.93,0:21:12.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,yet survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:14.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's something to be happy about!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:15.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right, Kirara?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.74,0:21:20.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, Kagome? How is Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:24.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The herbs are taking effect.\NHis fever is down and he's sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:27.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going to gather more herbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:30.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right, Kirara and I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.75,0:21:33.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Cuz we're the healthiest ones\naround right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:37.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you, Shippo, Kirara.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:48.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo handed Naraku the\NSacred Jewel fragment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.47,0:21:52.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo who had died once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.57,0:21:57.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo who arose again\nwith a body made of clay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:21:59.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo who hates me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:01.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo who tried to kill Kagome.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:08.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where are you, my Kikyo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.96,0:23:51.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo had given Naraku the\NSacred Jewel fragment...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.59,0:23:52.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,she stole from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.99,0:23:54.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's power increases steadily...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.69,0:23:56.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and he sends offshoots of himself\nafter Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.26,0:24:00.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The mind-reading demon, Goshinki,\nsinks his fangs into Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.33,0:24:02.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! Inuyasha will lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.64,0:24:05.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just then, an evil aura\nenvelopes Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.51,0:24:08.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, what's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.04,0:24:12.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Tetsusaiga Breaks!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.31,0:24:14.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
